Train Ticket Assistance System
------------------------------

This project is a serverless train ticket assistance application that enables customers to:

--> Book Tickets – Collect passenger details and generate a unique ticket ID.
--> Cancel Tickets – Allow users to cancel existing bookings.
--> Check Ticket Details – Retrieve booking information using the ticket ID.
--> Connect with Customer Support – Provide an option for users to reach support.

Architecture & Technologies
---------------------------

--> AWS Lambda – Handles backend logic such as generating ticket IDs and Fetch user details.
--> Amazon DynamoDB – Stores user and ticket details in a scalable NoSQL database.
--> Integration – Lambda functions interact with DynamoDB for CRUD operations.
Features:

- Unique ticket ID generation.
- Secure and efficient data storage.
- Real-time ticket status retrieval.
